 
<p>
  Secretary Becerra says that <a href="https://www.cnn.com/2022/07/11/health/federal-abortion-law-preempts-state-law/index.html">federal law overrides state abortion bans</a>
  when an abortion is needed for a medical emergency.
<p>
  This will remove the most dangerous aspect of those bans &mdash; if the
  fanatics on the Supreme Court do not invent an excuse to strike it
  down.  It is hard to be confident that there is a limit they respect.

 